title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The FIB Files
content:
Master your hacking, infiltrating, and technical sabotage skills in The FIB Files. Jodi requires your expertise to snatch up valuables and vehicles to sell to buyers around Los Santos.

Purchase the Garment Factory from Maze Bank Foreclosures or the “For Sale” sign outside the property. You can then start the operations from the computer in the factory or anywhere on the Map using the new Darnell Inc iFruit App.
